{
  "text": "The detail description of the PPC has been published in [CITATION_1] . Here, we briefly recall that the PPC is a tool allowing the generation of the plane wave between its plates from DC up to the cutoff frequency of the first higher propagation mode T E 10 . The plates are made of aluminium and joined by two tapered parts. The cell can be seen as a microstrip transmission line where the substrate is the air, therefore the characteristic impedance, as well as the cutoff frequency of such line, depend on its dimensions.",
  "citation_candidates": [
